Package net.sf.ntru.demo

Contains sample and benchmark programs

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AesExample
    Demonstrates how to encrypt data that is longer than the maximum message length for pure NTRUEncrypt (see EncryptionParameters.getMaxMessageLength()).
    Benchmark
    Benchmarks NTRUEncrypt against ECC and RSA.
    SimpleExample
    A simple program demonstrating the use of NtruEncrypt and NtruSign.
    Timings
